				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">
<br />
...oh and um what is the bstlords atk buff? and im not sure but does it really beat shamans avatar??...
<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Short answer, yes. Long answer:
<br />

<br />
Comparison of Beastlord's Savagery / Ferocity to Shaman's Avatar / Ferine Avatar:
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Ferocity:</span>(65 Beastlord)
<br />

<br />
Effects :
<br />

<br />
Increase Stamina by 40 (L65)
<br />
Decrease Stamina Loss by 10 (L65)
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Increase Attack (ATK) by 150 (L65)
<br />
Increase All Resists by 65 (L65)</span>
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Ferine Avatar:</span>(65 Shaman)
<br />

<br />
Effects :
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Increase Attack (ATK) by 140 (L65)</span>
<br />
Increase Agility by 140 (L65)
<br />
Increase Strength by 140 (L65)
<br />
Increase Dexterity by 140 (L65)
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Savagery:</span>(60 Beastlord)
<br />

<br />
 Effects :
<br />

<br />
Increase Stamina by 25 (L60)
<br />
Decrease Stamina Loss by 10 (L60)
<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Increase Attack (ATK) by 100 (L60)
<br />
Increase All Resists by 50 (L60)</span>
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Avatar:</span>(60 Shaman)
<br />

<br />
Effects :
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-style: italic">Increase Attack (ATK) by 100 (L60)</span>
<br />
Increase Agility by 100 (L60)
<br />
Increase Strength by 100 (L60)
<br />
Increase Dexterity by 100 (L60)
<br />

<br />
Add to this that the Beastlord's Spiritual Vigor:
<br />

<br />
Increase Attack (ATK) by 40 (L62)
<br />
Increase Total Hit Points by 225 (L62)
<br />

<br />
Stacks with their Ferocity / Savagery, a Beastlord can effectively add 190 ATK, and 225 hitpoints. 50 ATK, 225 hitpoints over a shaman's ferine avatar.
<br />

<br />
This is <span style="font-weight: bold">strictly</span> a comparison between the two classes as far as boosting attack, to answer the above quoted question. I have no opinion on their list of improvements, as I don't play a shaman as a main.<br />_________________<br /><span style="font-weight: bold">
<br />
Mistomeer C'Dyarnt
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=378575" target="_blank" class="postlink">Arch Convoker</a></span></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
