				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If I may add, SCS does *little* to help with the agro from DoT spells.  Poison has very high agro.  FP + BoT = agro, even if the mob is at 35% health.  That is why FD is quite powerful, even more powerful than concussion/boggle.  FD = The ability to turn on/off agro at will, not just lower it.
<br />

